    Tune is in the beta phase and as such, you won't be charged for events. We'll let you
    know when it exits the beta phase.
  </p>
  <h3>API keys</h3>
  <p>
    Your API keys are located at
    <a href="{{= it.context.APP_URL }}/profile">app.tune/settings</a>.
  </p>
